title: Alfred v2.0.9 [Zeus Downloads]
description:
Alfred v2.0.9
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://www.alfredapp.com/


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "Alfred v2.0.9.dmg".
- Drag/Copy "Alfred 2.app" to your "Applications" folder.
- Open "Patch.app".
- Drag "Alfred 2" from your "Applications" folder on to the Patch. You should see a message that should say Patching Successful.
- Thats it, you now have a fully functional copy of Alfred 2.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update Alfred 2 as updating it might cause a problem. You have been warned.
